headline: A Look At Centene (CNC) Valuation After Barclays Upgrade On ACA Margin Expansion
summary: Barclays’ upgrade of Centene (CNC) to Overweight, tied to expected margin expansion in the Affordable Care Act market, has put fresh attention on the insurer’s pricing power and recent share performance. See our latest analysis for Centene. That upgrade comes after a sharp swing in sentiment, with a 30 day share price return of 23.21% and a 90 day share price return of 31.21% contrasting with a 1 year total shareholder return decline of 25.72%. This suggests recent momentum is rebuilding...
